PrecisOrder giving notice of the National Guideline for SEALANTS AND CAULKING COMPOUNDS (ECP-45-92) specifying that certified products must not be formulated with aromatic solvents, fibrous talc or asbestos, formaldehyde, halogenated solvents or compounds of mercury, lead, cadmium and hexavalent chromium and limiting the amount of volatile organic compounds within the product formulation to 20.0 g/Litre.
Attachments
precis:
Order giving notice of the National Guideline for SEALANTS AND CAULKING
COMPOUNDS (ECP-45-92) specifying that certified products must not be
formulated with aromatic solvents, fibrous talc or asbestos, formaldehyde,
halogenated solvents or compounds of mercury, lead, cadmium and hexavalent
chromium and limiting the amount of volatile organic compounds within the
product formulation to 20.0 g/Litre.
